<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē sōmaratnagrahapatiga
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇitē jyēṣṭhamāsē daśamyāṁ śuklāyāṁ
<lb n="3"/>jīvavārē hariśikharipatērdīpanaivēdya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>hētō<unclear>ḥ</unclear> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>yaḥ</unclear> prādādvyōmayugmāvani
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śaśi<unclear>ga</unclear>ṇitā naicikīḥ puṇyasiddhyai (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) sa śrī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mānarjunākhyakṣitipatiravatāt bhūmi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mācaṁdratāraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavaruṣaṁbulu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>1291 gunēṁṭi jyēṣṭa vimala daśami
<lb n="9" break="no"/>yu guruvāramunāṁḍu O
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍḍavādi Arjunadēvarāju tanaku nabhīṣṭārtthasi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ddiga śrīnarasihyanāthunisannidhini Akhaṁ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḍadīpālu 8 veluṁguṭakuṁ beṭṭina mō
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dālu 836 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nityamunnu māpaṭi Avasara
<lb n="14" break="no"/>maṁdu pālāragiṁpaṁ beṭṭina <unclear>mō</unclear>dalu 263 
<lb n="15"/>Iṁtavaṭṭu dharmmuvu Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyi
<lb n="16" break="no"/>gāṁ beṭṭenu Ī dharmmupu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa
<lb n="17"/>Ī pālatōḍanu Aidu talyalu Arjunabhōga
<lb n="18" break="no"/>mugānu nityamunnurātri Āragiṁvanu tō
<lb n="19" break="no"/>rānapolamu padipuṭṭu Ācaṁdrākkasthāyigā
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṁ beṭṭenu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrīśrī
</p>

